trong>.<\/p>\n<p>Thanks to our brilliant team of chefs, front of house staff, runners and organisers; we were able to deliver fantastic quality food bang on time!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our dedicated team smashed it for another year at one of the most challenging festival catering operations on the circuit.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13886,"featured_media":9318,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[27,11],"tags":[298,304,305],"class_list":["post-9317","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-festivals","category-latest-blog-postings","tag-festival","tag-festival-catering","tag-focus"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Focus on Focus: Large-scale festival catering with military precision - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/focus-on-focus-large-scale-festival-catering-with-military-precision\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Focus on Focus: Large-scale festival catering with military precision - Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Our dedicated team smashed it for another year at one of the most challenging festival catering operations on the circuit.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/focus-on-focus-large-scale-festival-catering-with-military-precision\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2019-08-05T20:44:19+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:modified_time\"